{
  "stem": "26983.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was the beginning of deportation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was one of the first--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- the beginning of a kind of deportation of Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Eichmann was the leader of this--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Was in charge of this operation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Operation, but--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was built.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was nothing there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the Jews from Mahrisch-Ostrau, they called it Umschulung.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They want reeducate them or re-- give them other profession.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, it was '39, soon after the occupation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that was something very curious.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father said, I don't need another occupation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I have a good occupation.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I can do things from leather and so on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he hit himself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean he didn't went to the call.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I remember--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, only men.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And only men who were not, maybe, high officials in the Jewish community, were not teachers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were not in this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they took all the men.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, he was in that category, but just he didn't went to it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was, of course, very dangerous.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he called a Czech doctor just to have a kind of--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Certificate.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That he has a cold or so.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was, of course, just a bluff.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And after only a week or so, he slowly went on the street.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Again, he showed himself, and we were very, very afraid, first of all, that somebody could denounce him.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we knew there are people, even some of the Jews, who were denouncing-- who were working with the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I remember even the story that somebody met him on the street and said, Mr.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Bakon, you are alive?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I heard that you died in Nisko.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there were all kinds of rumors, of course.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Did any from-- anyone from your family go to Nisko, your uncles?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From my-- because--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
